headline: Wynn Resorts (WYNN) Expands Global Footprint With UAE Mega-Resort, JPMorgan Raises Price Target
summary: Wynn Resorts, Limited (NASDAQ:WYNN) ranks among the best sin stocks to buy in 2026.
